                    "human thing, scoured, seen clean",
                    "through from here to an iron heaven.",
                    "",
                    "A place where things",
                    "were said and done,",
                    "there you can remember",
                    "what you need to",
                    "remember. Melancholy is useful. Bring yours.",
                    "There are no neighbors to wonder",
